notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-21T18:28:00.462Z",claude-code-agent,"Implemented on branch feat/sdk-invoke-search-vector-migration-pm-bd3u (PR #330). Added three SDK invoke helpers in src/sdk/testing.ts plus barrel exports in src/sdk/index.ts. runRegisteredSearchProviderForTest dispatches query/embed/embedBatch/queryExpansion/rerank with camelCase+snake_case alias resolution via SEARCH_PROVIDER_OPERATION_DEFINITION_KEYS. runRegisteredVectorStoreAdapterForTest dispatches query/upsert/delete. runRegisteredMigrationForTest resolves by id through assertRegisteredMigration then invokes getMigrationRuntimeDefinition(migration).run with a host-shaped SchemaMigrationRunContext. All three invoke runtime_definition (the live-function clone), not definition (which stringifies functions). Verification: typecheck green, full coverage 4822 tests 100/100/100/100, static-quality + docs gates green, manual smoke of built dist/sdk/testing.js and a temp-workspace CLI flow. 6 new specs in tests/unit/sdk/sdk-index.spec.ts (operation happy paths, alias resolution, unregistered + unimplemented-operation guards, migration default-status + runless paths, barrel equivalence). Docs updated in docs/SDK.md and docs/EXTENSIONS.md."
body: ""
